OL,3,CCampaigner Zack Kerr plans fundraising
OL,4,Cfootball game in aid of 'unsung heroes'
OL,6,FA campaigner is swapping petitions for
OL,7,Fthe football pitch as he prepares to
OL,8,Fhost a special charity match in
OL,9,FAccrington.
OL,11,FZack Kerr, 26, who led the nationwide
OL,12,FChanging Places campaign and was named
OL,13,Fa winner at the National Diversity
OL,14,FAwards, has organised the big day to
OL,15,Fraise funds for the North West
OL,16,FAmbulance Service charity.
OL,18,FThe cause is close to his heart after
OL,19,Fparamedics helped save his mum's life
OL,20,Fwhen she suffered a shock heart attack
OL,21,Flast year.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
