OL,3,CCampaigner Zack Kerr plans fundraising
OL,4,Cfootball game in aid of 'unsung heroes'
OL,6,FSpeaking to Katie on ITV Granada
OL,7,FReports, Zack said the ambulance crews
OL,8,Fwere "unsung heroes" and and said his
OL,9,Fmum, Krissy, is now recovering well `
OL,10,Fand even helping him organise the
OL,11,Fevent.
OL,13,FThe match takes place on 2 May at
OL,14,FAccrington Stanley's football ground.
OL,16,FZack said fans can look forward to a
OL,17,Fpolice versus ambulance showdown,
OL,18,Ffollowed by a celebrity team taking on
OL,19,Fformer Accrington Stanley players -
OL,20,Fplus a mascot race for good measure.
OL,26,@pD@FOUpD@TO]
