OL,3,CCampaigner Zack Kerr plans fundraising
OL,4,Cfootball game in aid of 'unsung heroes'
OL,6,FGates open at noon, with a suggested
OL,7,Fdonation on entry.
OL,9,FZack, who is an Honorary Freeman of
OL,10,FHyndburn, hopes to raise #10,000 for
OL,11,Fvital equipment and support services
OL,12,Ffor the charity.
OL,14,F"Let's all have a great day for a
OL,15,Fgreat cause," he said.
OL,17,FFor more information click here.
OL,26,@vD@AOUwD@MO]
